ing: 1 (15.25 ounce) can sweet white whole kernel corn, undrained
1 (8.5 ounce) package dry corn muffin mix (such as JiffyÂ®)
des: "Sweet corn casserole reminiscent of the corn tamales served at Chevy's Fresh MexÂ® restaurant."
ins:
Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C).
Combine whole kernel corn, cream-style corn, muffin mix, onion, butter, eggs, and red bell pepper in a 2-quart casserole dish; stir.
Bake in preheated oven until golden brown and the center is set, about 1 hour.
